SUB_W02_EVAR_MIDO_LITA_YELLOW_CASTLE_020.text:
There's just no way she could be a golem!
C'mon, let's go talk to the Yellow Sage;
I'm sure she'll know something.

SUB_W02_EVAR_MIDO_LITA_YELLOW_CASTLE_040.text:
She does not wish the girl to fail;
she will pretend not to notice even
if she does catch wind of our scheme.

SUB_W02_EVAR_MIDO_LITA_COLOR_QUEST_WHITE.text:
We'll get lost if we aren't careful;
not even I know how big this place is. Oh, and don't let your guard down,
or you'll be eaten by one of these plants.

SUB_W02_EVAR_MIDO_LITA_COLOR_QUEST_RED_0.text:
This is the Squire's Burg, where they all live.
All witches have to respect them here;
the others get cranky if you don't.

SUB_W02_FUNC_MIDO_LITA_OUTPOST_CONTROL_1.text:
There's no use worrying too much about it;
you can't be in two places at once, after all.
Just make the call and go.

SUB_W02_EVAR_MIDO_BRILLIANTTOWER_000_CUT.text:
I, um... I don't think I did anything quite
so worthy of your praise, Arch Witch;
he's actually a rather odd little man.

SUB_W02_EVAR_MIDO_WHITE_000_CUT_000_040.text:
Ah, but perhaps it is inevitable;
the Conjoined Worlds ever seek
equilibrium, after all.

SUB_W02_EVAR_MIDO_RED_000_CUT_000_020.text:
Is that so? Well, you ought do as you like;
he doesn't seem strong enough to cause
any real harm.
